snippet.textDisplay: PRETTY BABY MAGAZINE.  A MAGAZINE FOR INDIE TRASH.  EACH COVER WE MAKE A T SHIRT WITH TYPE THAT IS THEN PHOTOGRAPHED FOR THE MAGAZINE COVER.  THIS WEEKS EDITION A PICTURE OF SHIRLEY MC CLAINE AND THE TYPE READS "WHO KNEW COVID WOULD EXTEND INTO THE NEXT LIFE>"
